{"tid":2235028,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"售貨員協助掘磚人士搬磚 今判社會服務令100小時 並向康文署賠償316元","createTime":"2020-10-08T10:51:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T10:56:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f96f54aa4f797dea8019de935d09f881c56b71f9","tid":2235028,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T10:51:22.000Z","msg":"售貨員去年11月在秀茂坪參加摺紙鶴靜坐後，應邀到附近休憩處，並替掘磚人士搬磚，終與另外兩人被捕。該兩人早前獲准簽保守行為，售貨員則承認刑事損壞罪。主任裁判官徐綺薇今判刑時指，涉案磚頭明顯有機會用作堵路等非法用途，不能忽視被告行為招致的風險，最終判被告須履行100小時社會服務令，並向康文署賠償316元。<br />\n<br />\n辯方今指，被告的感化報告內容正面，冀法庭接受感化官建議，判被告感化。徐官引述報告指，被告向感化官稱有悔意，自知掘磚及搬磚屬違法，故案發時曾猶豫是否參與。感化官認為，被告適合接受感化令或社會服務令，被告亦願意接納。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，警員當晚乘警車路經現場時，發現有人掘路，遂下車追捕，截獲被告與同案兩名分別14及17歲的少年。案件上次提堂時，控方考慮兩名少年的年齡後，同意對兩人撤控，法庭批准兩人各自簽2,000元、守行為一年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201008/UDW777OFOVF6TLZWOLQPYJPWFY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2FUDW777OFOVF6TLZWOLQPYJPWFY%2F&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr94xWyFD0xakOW3kliQQxS8%3D&h=255860b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2FUDW777OFOVF6TLZWOLQPYJPWFY%2F&h=613e5e70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201008/UDW777OFOVF6TLZWOLQPYJPWFY/</a>"},{"pid":"42547d7170bb3c58478bea39bfd7c10f9e87983a","tid":2235028,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T10:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6505dd3e276df14f3cfa93e996c1b381ae1346e","tid":2235028,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T10:56:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}